						key="staticText-83"/>
					<box></box>
					<textElement>
						<font size="12"/>
					</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[This order is issued subject to recovery of all the dues from the deceased person before settlement of death benefits and if any dues are found to be recoverable from the deceased  person at a later date, the person who furnished the “No Due Certificate” will be held responsible and action will be taken against him and he will be held liable for the unrecovered amount if any.]]></text>
				</staticText>
